==English==
===Noun phrase===
'''time travel''' (''[[uncountable]]'')

#[[Hypothetical]] or [[fictional]] [[travel]] at will to a [[time]] in the [[past]] or the [[future]], typically by means of a machine (a [[time machine]]) or a [[wormhole]].  However, due to complications, your safety may not be guaranteed, unless you push it to the limit.


